      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-07-29T05:07:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think I\u0027d be OK with this change. Yes, the func might panic, but I doubt it will cause actual problems in production - it would mean the developer did not write tests whosoever, in which case the code is more likely to fail in different ways.\n\nmarking unresolved since the discussion is ongoing.",
      "parentUuid": "6a6702b6_8603efb3",
      "revId": "9cf8dce9c5ea34498dc338ef7f334b92974490da",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
